race.description: Goanna Graphics Country Boosted Mdn Handicap
race.comment: WONDERFUL MISTAKE (10) resumes and three back, she was just nudged out at Canberra on debut. Went close there following and then was spelled off a plainer run in tougher company at Wagga. She will be naturally improved, and the in-form Boudvillain rides from a low barrier. Positions forward, and a bold return is likely. Wary of BRASS MONKEYS (4) on debut. He's trialled sharply at Goulburn and Canberra, and Heywood stays aboard from the latest. Looks to have plenty of ability and is ready to go. HAZ STYLES (9) has a wide gate to manage, but gets the go-to jockey around these parts. Peaks off a Wagga placing and can make the finish with average luck in transit. SPY TRADER (5) didn't show a lot in his only trial coming in, but races for a stable who love targeting these carnivals. Watch for any market moves.
